{"tid":1212813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳建制派11am重返立會大樓 警員場外清空路障持盾戒備","createTime":"2019-06-12T22:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T00:20:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f4463b72822d7af48689f41408d8f96453b93b","tid":1212813,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:28:38.000Z","msg":"原定於周三舉行的立法會大會中，將會就《逃犯條例》修訂進行二讀，惟在數以萬計市民包圍下，最終決定暫停，有消息指建制派已預備周四（6月13日）早上11時返回大樓開會，但會議能否舉行，仍要視乎建制派屆時是否有足夠人數返抵立法會大樓。《果燃台》屆時將會直播，另外，《蘋果》亦會直擊場外最新狀況。<br />\n早上約6時記者到政總附近視察，發現現場有不少持槍持盾警員巡邏，但就暫時未見有市民出現。另外亦有警員負責清走昨日由市民築起的路障。立法會行政署發出通知，指今日（6月13日）及明日（6月14日）政府總部暫停開放，立法會職員毋需上班工作，訪客活動亦會延期或取消。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190613/large/1560377453_c7ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190613%2Flarge%2F1560377453_c7ab.jpg&h=32c8ecfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190613/59709258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59709258&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=c78f53a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59709258&h=0818ddc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190613/59709258</a>"},{"pid":"c8d25a5d46d6b370a4b91cc85e306cece3f81135","tid":1212813,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18e49d9e502dfcc734c0cd45e70c6a0da2566b1","tid":1212813,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:30:20.000Z","m